    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find for a discerning buyer. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously maintained, from the flawless original paint and pristine interior to the high-performance engine that runs like new. There are no mechanical issues, cosmetic blemishes, or wear patterns to speak of; it drives and looks exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfect example of this model that needs nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 48500.0,
